sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Gracz
    participant WS as WebSocket Gateway
    participant GE as Game Engine
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    P->>WS: table.join {tableId, seatIndex}
    WS->>GE: assignSeat()
    GE-->>P: table.state

    Note over GE: Stół zapełniony + krupier obecny
    GE-->>P: round.started {roundId}

    P->>WS: bet.place {amount}
    WS->>GE: validateBet()
    GE->>DB: UPDATE wallet — odejmij zakład
    GE-->>P: bet.placed

    GE->>GE: dealInitialCards()
    GE-->>P: card.dealt
    GE-->>P: player.turn

    P->>WS: action.hit / action.stand
    GE->>GE: dealerPlay()
    GE-->>P: dealer.turn
    GE-->>P: round.result
    GE->>DB: UPDATE wallet — payout
    GE-->>P: round.settled
    GE-->>P: table.state {status: waiting}
